rce-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n<br />\n未簽嘅快D簽。請廣傳！"},{"pid":"77003d2b442c986c1af76b004f2dc931b5a9e995","tid":1536671,"uid":310397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:56:10.000Z","msg":"話fake news嘅睇下tg channel啦"},{"pid":"2ebd98ebb807fd471947655fff730cd081d73da7","tid":1536671,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:57:29.000Z","msg":"全民皆兵，破釜沉舟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n同我推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武裝起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a212bf9198242ef805eb6cf954307951813ef4c2","tid":1536671,"uid":88768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">太子殺人犯</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1669 鍾國恩 警長<br />\n48958 李彼得 高級警員<br />\n54538 張文麟 高級警員<br />\n58248 梁智顯 高級警員 <br />\n52080 張達雄 高級警員<br />\n再加 8692 (未confirm)<br />\n<br />\n一定要推阿！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n推！！太子有片 六個殺人犯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536563\" data-auto-link targ